==English==

===Etymology===
Compare German ''[[bäen]]''; an imitative word.

===Noun===
'''baa''', plural '''baas'''
*[[IPA]]: /bæ/, plural /bæz/

#The [[characteristic]] [[cry]] or [[bleating]] of a [[sheep]].

====Synonyms====
*[[baaing]]
*[[bleat]]
*[[bleating]]

