===Intransitive verb===
'''baa'''
*[[IPA]]: /bæː/ ''or'' /bɑː/

#Of a sheep, to make its characteristic cry.
#:He treble '''baas''' for help, but none can get. - Sir [[w:Philip Sidney|Philip Sidney]]
